# Pybind11 Coding Standards

- **REQUIRED**: Use explicit return types on lambdas/callables in `.def()` or `m.def()` (e.g. `-> bool`, `-> py::list`).
- Expose C++ methods under **snake_case** in Python (e.g. `ShouldRun` → `should_run`).
